<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>  Hey guys.  I have been exploring droga for the past two days with a level 49 druid friend of mine.  After we got him a shroud of nature we decided to go after the soothsayer for a mantle for me.<BR>
  4 spawns in the room it was a little tough to break, im a level 45 chanter so i had to mez and charm ect..but we ended up on top and it was smooth sailing from then on, our level 50 warrior friend finally got back with us and it got pretty boring.<BR>
  The first two times we killed the soothesayer he dropped an earring.  Since i came there for the mantle i was a little suprised that his rare dropped two times in a row .  He spawns next to the stove (if you are standing next to the bed and facing out it is on the right side) he is a shaman and summons a pet if left alive long enough. We killed him 3 out of 5 spawns and i got my mantle. =) im on the fennin Ro server and am looking to trade or sell the earring-goodluck guys<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
