<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I got the Earring on a raid in Droga lastnight. Room wasn't overly difficult to break, but getting there was a real pain. The tunnels on the way are filled with goblins, and they have a fast respawn rate.<BR>
<BR>
Soothsayer Drezgek spawned about 1 in 3 that night, the rest of the time having a Goblin Taskmaster, Legate or Adept spawn in his place (which is in the corner by the Oven, btw). Dropped the Earring twice, and the Mantle three times.</font></td></tr></table>
